Hello, and welcome to the final module of this course on JSON with Java.

2
00:00:05.946 --> 00:00:06.991
In this module,

3
00:00:06.991 --> 00:00:10.873
you're going to learn more about integrating JSON with existing web

4
00:00:10.873 --> 00:00:13.800
frameworks and also cover a few summary topics.

5
00:00:13.800 --> 00:00:16.517
This will help you save time and be more productive when

6
00:00:16.517 --> 00:00:19.801
using the most common Java frameworks.

7
00:00:19.801 --> 00:00:23.661
We're going to cover a couple of key integration points in this module.

8
00:00:23.661 --> 00:00:27.139
Firstly, we're going to look at how to integrate JSON parsing with Spring,

9
00:00:27.139 --> 00:00:30.663
a very popular framework for web development.

10
00:00:30.663 --> 00:00:33.927
